{"tid":249221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真．NMB48討論區22:Members助養計劃","createTime":"2017-05-19T06:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T07:02:48.000Z","uid":2660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"831e25ef4bc5729d5057d206b21f2e4057b8afa4","tid":249221,"uid":2660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T06:54:57.000Z","msg":"NMB48是一個由秋元康擔任製作人，以日本近畿地方為主要活動中心的女性偶像團體。2010年創立的NMB48是繼SKE48之後，第二個根據AKB48的概念而創立的地方性姊妹團體，主要的幕後營運業者是以大阪為主要根據地的娛樂經濟公司吉本興業旗下的企業&mdash;Showtitle(ショータイトル)。<br />\n<br />\nNMB48的團體名稱源自位於大阪南區的鬧區難波（其羅馬拼音為「NAMBA」），大部分的成員都出身自近畿與中國地方一帶的縣分。 由於即將結束營運,NMB48於2016年並沒獲邀出場年末的NHK紅白歌合戰，17th單亦發售無期。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">16th Single - 「僕以外の誰か」已於12月28日發售！</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">通常盤 Type-A</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.nmb48.com/images/discography/img_cd16th_b01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmb48.com%2Fimages%2Fdiscography%2Fimg_cd16th_b01.jpg&h=5102f5cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">通常盤 Type-B</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.nmb48.com/images/discography/img_cd16th_b02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmb48.com%2Fimages%2Fdiscography%2Fimg_cd16th_b02.jpg&h=df8df22c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">通常盤 Type-C</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.nmb48.com/images/discography/img_cd16th_b03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmb48.com%2Fimages%2Fdiscography%2Fimg_cd16th_b03.jpg&h=1327f2b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">通常盤 Type-D</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.nmb48.com/images/discography/img_cd16th_b04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmb48.com%2Fimages%2Fdiscography%2Fimg_cd16th_b04.jpg&h=19e2fbab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">劇場盤</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.nmb48.com/images/discography/img_cd16th_b05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmb48.com%2Fimages%2Fdiscography%2Fimg_cd16th_b05.jpg&h=d548fb35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6d8a0f2b905929b62e2a8ec892caaaf3bf88551","tid":249221,"uid":2660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T06:56:07.000Z","msg":"【MV】僕以外の誰か(Short ver.) / NMB48[公式]<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2LCoB-jdBPQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2LCoB-jdBPQ&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=4078e302\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2LCoB-jdBPQ</a><br />\n<br />\n【MV】僕以外の誰か(日下このみダンシングバージョン) / NMB48[公式]<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EZunBX4VXrI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEZunBX4VXrI&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=5370f634\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EZunBX4VXrI</a><br />\n<br />\n【MV】 孤独ギター(Short ver.) / NMB48 team N[公式]<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kuT7O4e5ulE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkuT7O4e5ulE&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=0c451d86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kuT7O4e5ulE</a><br />\n<br />\n【MV】恋は災難(Short ver.) / NMB48 team M[公式]<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=deN1qyW5N2I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdeN1qyW5N2I&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=d15115c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=deN1qyW5N2I</a><br />\n<br />\n【MV】Let it snow !(Short ver.) / NMB48 team BII[公式]<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j7uFx6schCA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dj7uFx6schCA&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRh