<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">研究生</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgsafe.org/808fd6b0a7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgsafe.org%2F808fd6b0a7.png&h=020d11cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3be30fc861f61a6914f7b83bdf82b812a3189d2b","tid":249221,"uid":2660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T06:58:31.000Z","msg":"簡易抽握手會or大寫真 步驟 by Nagisayaka <br />\n<br />\nstep 1: 有日本地址 (e.g. 轉運/日本朋友) <br />\nstep 2: 劇場盤抽選開始,選擇自己想握既mb/影既team <br />\nstep 3: submit (submit左就冇得改) <br />\nstep 4: 抽完有結果,中選同落選都會有email話你知 (<del>迷路同</del>彩就基本上一輪就滿) <br />\nstep 4.1: 第一輪通常會用黎抽晒大top先,之後再抽冇咁易爆部既mb <br />\nstep 4.2: 通常出碟之前會有幾輪抽選,完左會一次過寄比你 <br />\nstep 5: 比錢 <br />\nstep 6: 等收碟,握手/影相卷會一齊寄比你 <br />\nstep 7: 轉運收到後睇下自己仲有冇野買,冇就寄返香港 <br />\nstep 8: 收貨 <br />\nstep 9: 帶埋d卷去日本參加握手/影相會 <br />\nstep 10: 渡過愉快既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抽NMB48個別握手會詳盡教學by中左自己推生誕祭既Mr_Snowman巴打<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://come2jp.com/idol/2016/09/21/nmb48握手會抽選方法/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcome2jp.com%2Fidol%2F2016%2F09%2F21%2Fnmb48%E6%8F%A1%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%8A%BD%E9%81%B8%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=2b3bd650\" target=\"_blank\">http://come2jp.com/idol/2016/09/21/nmb48握手會抽選方法/</a><br />\n\f"},{"pid":"3bfa34451a81c0d60c8d342613efdde4d2e1ff81","tid":249221,"uid":2660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T06:58:58.000Z","msg":"NMB48 mobile mail (モバイルメール)申請網址<br />\n<a href=\"http://sp.mail.nmb48.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsp.mail.nmb48.com%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=d1fd00fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sp.mail.nmb48.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n可以用credit card比錢<br />\n每日每位mb只需10.8円 港幣都係6，7毫<br />\n一齊嚟助養佢地 <br />\n<br />\n開post所需文件<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-dn4DBQoFfSBTn2LdcjCaoi_r4hsoBOTVTzTbjvbafE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1-dn4DBQoFfSBTn2LdcjCaoi_r4hsoBOTVTzTbjvbafE&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=50a8dcc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-dn4DBQoFfSBTn2LdcjCaoi_r4hsoBOTVTzTbjvbafE</a>\f"},{"pid":"8fd125f76f4352f5db2f37f2b165d309bde87c44","tid":249221,"uid":6390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:02:37.000Z","msg":"開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61617c2a9c9457cdd4675adc2ebc5083b2284435","tid":249221,"uid":2660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:02:48.000Z","msg":"畢業予定: <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://48pedia.org/images/thumb/0/0e/2016%E5%B9%B4NMB48%E3%83%97%E3%83%AD%E3%83%95%E3%82%A3%E3%83%BC%E3%83%AB_%E8%97%A4%E6%B1%9F%E3%82%8C%E3%81%84%E3%81%AA.jpg/250px-2016%E5%B9%B4NMB48%E3%83%97%E3%83%AD%E3%83%95%E3%82%A3%E3%83%BC%E3%83%AB_%E8%97%A4%E6%B1%9F%E3%82%8C%E3%81%84%E3%81%AA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F48pedia.org%2Fimages%2Fthumb%2F0%2F0e%2F2016%25E5%25B9%25B4NMB48%25E3%2583%2597%25E3%2583%25AD%25E3%2583%2595%25E3%2582%25A3%25E3%2583%25BC%25E3%2583%25AB_%25E8%2597%25A4%25E6%25B1%259F%25E3%2582%258C%25E3%2581%2584%25E3%2581%25AA.jpg%2F250px-2016%25E5%25B9%25B4NMB48%25E3%2583%2597%25E3%2583%25AD%25E3%2583%2595%25E3%2582%25A3%25E3%2583%25BC%25E3%2583%25AB_%25E8%2597%25A4%25E6%25B1%259F%25E3%2582%258C%25E3%2581%2584%25E3%2581%25AA.jpg&h=b5fd44d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">藤江れいな (AKB48 4期生 チームBII所屬)</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/30/012740_022f80ce4e4d0b3087697e1aa0b5d366.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F30%2F012740_022f80ce4e4d0b3087697e1aa0b5d366.jpg&h=2ef8872c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">西仲七海(ドラフト2期生 チームM研究生)</span>[/quote]"}]}